image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a staircase landing inside a building. On the wall, there are two fire extinguishers (one red, one black) mounted next to a sign that reads '3RD FLOOR'. There is a circular light fixture above the extinguishers and a smoke detector on the ceiling. To the left is a wooden handrail with blue metal balusters. The floor is carpeted in a dark grey grid pattern. A white framed map or document is visible on the right wall.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural shot looking up a short flight of stairs toward a landing.

notes: The image is a standard evidentiary photograph, likely part of a site inspection or investigation. The text '3RD FLOOR' identifies the location within the building.
